query:
INSERT INTO documents (tripId, name, category, fileUrl, fileKey, mimeType, tags, notes, coverImage, hotelId, createdAt, updatedAt)
SELECT 2 as tripId, name, category, fileUrl, fileKey, mimeType, tags, notes, coverImage, hotelId, NOW() as createdAt, NOW() as updatedAt
FROM documents
WHERE tripId = 1;
